      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i need some advice. my neighbor just changed their wifi name to \"SRY ABOUT THE NOISE\" and honestly it feels super targeted. every time i walk into my kitchen or the bathroom the signal on my phone just spikes like crazy. i think they're using the signal strength to track where i am in my house. what do you think?",
