      "content": "but it's not just the name. i've been watching it. every single time i walk past the hallway, the bars go from 2 to 4 instantly. like, it's way too consistent to be \"interference.\" and why would they name it that? it's like they're mocking me for existing in the apartment next to them. don't you think it's weird that the spikes happen exactly when i move around?",
