    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so intentional though. like, there's no way it's a coincidence that they picked that specific phrase right when i've been staying in more. if it's just \"trolling,\" why is it so precise with the signal? i feel like i'm being watched through the airwaves. do you think there's any way someone could actually use signal strength to map out a floor plan? like, is that even technically possible?",
